original: Kiarin, Eugen, distriktsveterinär, Vimmerby, f. 12/6/95 i Sthlm. G. 24 m. Eliy Lundström. Barn: Britta f. 25, Sven Gunnar 27, Torsten 29. — Stud:ex. i Ystad 15, veter :ex. 21. Assist. v. stat. veter :bakt. anst. 22-24, labor. där 24-29, distrrveter. i Vimmerby distr. fr. 29. Skr.: ett 20-tal meddel. o. upps. fr. stat. veter :bakt. anst. 22-29. Hobby: skytte.
translated: Kiarin, Eugen, district veterinarian, Vimmerby, b. 12/6/1895 in Stockholm. Married on 24th with Eliy Lundström. Children: Britta b. 1925, Sven Gunnar b. 1927, Torsten b. 1929. — Completed high school in Ystad in 1915, graduated as a veterinarian in 1921. Assistant at the state veterinary department 1922-1924, laboratory work there from 1924-1929. District veterinarian in Vimmerby district from 1929. Has written around 20 publications and articles from the state veterinary department 1922-1929. Hobby: shooting.
